snippet.title: Unworthy Pre-Alpha - Dark Sins
snippet.description:
We rise from our grave to see if we are worthy.

Unworthy is a hardcore combat-focused metroidvania without jumping. Still in the pre-alpha phase, I can see all of the major building blocks for a great game to be built around.

Check out the official site here: http://www.unworthygame.com/
